ğŸ“¦ Modules Overview
1. record.py
TemperatureRecord â€” A class representing daily temperature readings.

Methods:

convert_to(unit) â€” Converts between Celsius and Fahrenheit.

get_summary() â€” Returns summary statistics for the day.

2. converter.py
convert(value, from_unit, to_unit) â€” Converts a single temperature value.

3. analytics.py
average_temperature_across_days(records)

